attributionInfo.brokerName: Douglas Elliman Real Estate - The Sarkis Team
Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Stylish two-bedroom condo well located in the City Point section of South Boston. Initially converted in 2006, this unit is one of three in a charming Victorian Mansard. It features an open floor plan with a large granite island kitchen, maple cabinetry, stainless appliances, a gas fireplace, hardwood flooring, soaring ceilings, and a slider to a huge private deck. Both bedrooms are generously spacious, easily fitting king-size beds, offering comfort and luxury.  Other features/amenities include in-unit laundry, excellent closet space, storage in the basement, and a large shared yard. This location is steps to the Broadway shops, all bus lines, M Street beach, and minutes to the Seaport.
